        UC2[Control Pac-Man Movement]
        UC3[Pause Game]
        UC4[Resume Game]
        UC5[Restart Game]
        UC6[Quit Game]
        UC7[View Score]
        UC8[Eat Pellets]
        UC9[Eat Power Pellets]
        UC10[Eat Frightened Ghosts]
        UC11[Advance to Next Level]
        UC12[View Lives]
        UC13[Navigate Pause Menu]
        UC14[View Game Over Screen]
